# Systemic Insight (FAERS Context)

> Stimulant medications and certain antipsychotics, commonly prescribed for dopamine-related conditions, are associated with motivational deficits, dependency risks, and have been linked to **deaths and serious adverse events** in the FDA FAERS database (2020â€“2024). This module offers a non-pharmaceutical pathway to safely re-engage dopamine systems, using gentle, gamified personal care actions that rebuild motivation without overwhelm.

